<div class="mw-container">
  <h2 class="mw-section-title">About Me</h2>

  <div class="mw-grid-2 mw-mb-4">
    <!-- Profile Column -->
    <div>
      <div class="mw-avatar-container mw-d-flex mw-justify-center mw-my-5">
        <div class="mw-avatar mw-avatar-primary mw-avatar-xl">
          <img
            src="/assets/images/profile_photo.png"
            alt="Michael's profile photo"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mw-text-center">
        <h3 class="mw-mb-1">Michael Wellner</h3>
        <p class="mw-text-secondary">- Fullstack Developer -</p>
        <p />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bio Column -->
    <div>
      <p class="mw-mb-1">
        As a Fullstack Developer based in Stuttgart, Germany, and now in my late
        30s, my expertise lies in creating robust Java / Spring Boot backends,
        managing data via MySQL/Postgres and intuitive Angular frontends. I
        bring over a decade of experience focused on clean code, domain-driven
        design, and agile methodologies that lead to maintainable, scalable
        solutions. Additionally, I thrive in collaborative environments,
        utilizing standard industry tools like Git, IntelliJ, Jenkins, etc.
      </p>
      <p class="mw-mb-1">
        Throughout my career, I've specialized in developing microservice
        architectures that handle complex business requirements. I enjoy solving
        challenging technical problems - but always with the goal of delivering
        real, long-term value.
      </p>
      <p class="mw-mb-6">
        I believe in continuous learning, sharing knowledge, and mentoring the
        next generation of developers.
      </p>
      <blockquote>
        In the complex world of code, simplicity is the ultimate sophistication.
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tech Stack -->
  <div class="mw-grid-5 mw-mt-6">
    {% for element in stacks %}
    <div class="mw-card mw-card-stack">
      <div class="mw-card-stack-header">
        <div class="mw-card-stack-icon">
          <i class="{{ element.icon }}"></i>
        </div>
        <h5 class="mw-card-stack-title">{{ element.name }}</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="mw-card-stack-body">
        <p class="mw-card-stack-text">{{ element.text }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
